#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Bionic Space Expander"
msgstr "仿生空間擴展器"

#. ~ Description for Bionic Space Expander
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Introduces four new bionic implants that increase the available space for "
"bionic implementations. They're hard to find and expansive to build."
msgstr "引入四種新型仿生植入體，可增加可用於仿生植入的空間。它們難以尋覓且造價高昂。"
